move1.name: Sludge
move1.description: Unsanitary sludge is hurled at the target. It may also poison the target.

move2.name: Mud Bomb
move2.description: The user launches a glob of mud at the target. It may also lower the target's accuracy.

move3.name: Gunk Shot
move3.description: The user shoots filthy garbage at the target to attack. It may also poison the target.

move4.name: Dark Pulse
move4.description: The user releases a horrible aura imbued with dark thoughts. It may also make the target flinch.
